CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

April 5, 2010

[Cite as 04/05/2010 Case Announcements #2, 2010-Ohio-1527.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

1990-0291. State v. Durr.

Cuyahoga App. No. 57140. This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing of appellant’s motion for stay of execution scheduled for April 20, 2010.

It is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.

The late Chief Justice Thomas J. Moyer did not participate in the decision on this motion.
